trans-unit.source: Represents a configuration element that contains a key/value pair.
trans-unit.target: Representa un elemento de configuración que contiene un par clave/valor.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Configuration.KeyValueConfigurationElement> object inherits from the <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationElement> base class.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Configuration.KeyValueConfigurationElement> objeto hereda de la <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationElement> clase base.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationElement> object represents an element within a configuration file.
trans-unit.target: La <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationElement> objeto representa un elemento dentro de un archivo de configuración.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Configuration.KeyValueConfigurationElement> object can belong in a <xref:System.Configuration.KeyValueConfigurationCollection> collection.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Configuration.KeyValueConfigurationElement> objeto puede pertenecer a un <xref:System.Configuration.KeyValueConfigurationCollection> colección.
